msgstr "Gedetecteerde diensten"

#: includes/admin/review-setting.php:888
msgid ""
"TrustScript has detected the following services on your site. Configure "
"trigger statuses for each service to automatically collect reviews."
msgstr ""
"TrustScript heeft de volgende diensten op uw website gedetecteerd. Stel voor"
